sential qualities of an ideal candidate. Include previous work experience, education or achievements that would be beneficial. And list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Athletic Trainer requirements Bachelor Degree in Athletic Training, Master's preferred Computer skills to work with medical software Effective verbal and written communication skills 1 year of experience working in a clinical setting Required state certifications Ability to connect with patients Athletic Trainer related job titles: College Athletic Trainer Certified Athletic Trainer Athletic Therapist Senior Athletic Trainer Athletic Trainer (Part-Time) Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
